9	 *
10	 * PERF: This is a hot path - optimizations applied:
11	 * - Cache all property accesses at function start
12	 * - Use `| 0` instead of `|| 0` (bitwise coerces undefined to 0)
13	 * - Avoid optional chaining in inner loops
14	 * - Cache array references before mutation
